body:
Okay so being straight-forward here, I own all of the champions and Blue Shards are useless to me, I&#039;m sure many other people who&#039;ve been playing League for a while probably have all of the champs too. I was wondering if Riot could possibly add something else that we can do with Blue Shards other than using them to make champions, I&#039;m not sure how hard it would be to do that but I do think this would be a nice implementation to the Hextech Crafting System.

Thanks, 
Ace{{sticker:slayer-pantheon-thumbs}}
